Title: Designates a portion of the state highway system as the "Firefighter Peyton L. S. Morse Memorial Bridge"
Summary: Designates a portion of the state highway system as the "Firefighter Peyton L. S. Morse Memorial Bridge" in the town of Orleans, Jefferson county.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a portion of the state highway system as the "Firefighter Peyton L. S. Morse Memorial Bridge"
